highlights.text: “Bạn Thân Em” by Hữu Stream and Rocky CDE is the highest new entry on Viral Songs Vietnam at #3.
Ánh Sáng AZA has the most spots on Viral Songs Vietnam. “tâm trí lang thang” is the highest at #2.
“八方來財(Stacks from All Sides)” by 攬佬SKAI ISYOURGOD has been on Viral Songs Vietnam the longest, at 165 days straight.
“Nhân Danh Tình Yêu” by LYHAN is the biggest gainer on Viral Songs Vietnam, up 34 spots at #47.
